OL,5, The best-selling crime author Peter    
OL,6, Robinson has died at the age of 72, his
OL,7, publisher has confirmed.               
OL,9,FThe Leeds-born novelist was known for  
OL,10,Fthe DCI Alan Banks series of books, set
OL,11,Fin Yorkshire.                          
OL,13,FThe stories were adapted into an ITV   
OL,14,Fseries with Stephen Tompkinson, which  
OL,15,Fran from 2011 to 2017.                 
OL,17,FHis publisher said he had died after a 
OL,18,Fshort illness on Tuesday. Tributes have
OL,19,Fbeen paid by fellow crime writers Val  
OL,20,FMcDermid and Ian Rankin.               
